INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (206,1,'2025-03-26 09:40:02','2025-03-26 09:40:02','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Zakaat is a financial obligation in Islam for those who possess the minimum wealth to give <strong>2.5%</strong> of it to poor and needy Muslims. <br>Zakaat can<strong> only be given to Muslims. </strong><br>The Jamaat acts as an agent of Zakaat collection; we collect Zakaat from the members of the community who wish for it to be distributed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"700\",\"letterSpacing\":\"0.5px\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#343434\"}}},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#343434\"}},\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size\" style=\"color:#343434;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.5px\"><em>Abu Huraira reported Allah\'s Messenger (ﷺ) as saying that Allah, the Most Blessed and High, said: O son of Adam, spend. I will spend on you. The right hand of Allah is full and overflowing and in nothing would diminish it, by overspending day and night.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"700\",\"letterSpacing\":\"0.5px\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#343434\"}}},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#343434\"}},\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size\" style=\"color:#343434;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.5px\"><em>  (Sahih Muslim 993a)</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:quote {\"className\":\"is-style-plain\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-plain has-medium-font-size\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Frequently asked questions:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:details {\"style\":{\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"var:preset|color|black\"}}}},\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color\"><summary>What is Zakaat?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>Zakaat is a financial obligation in Islam for those who possess the minimum wealth to give 2.5% percent of it to poor and needy Muslims. <br>Zakaat can only be given to Muslims. <br>The Jamaat acts as an agent of Zakaat  collection; we collect Zakaat from the members of the community who wish for it to be distributed. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary>Am I eligible?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>To qualify, you must be a Muslim residing in Trinidad and Tobago, and be able to demonstrate that you are unable to afford your basic needs/monthly expenses. To confirm that you can receive assistance, we will review the financial information provided to us through your Zakaat application form. <br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary>What do I need to apply?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p><strong>All Zakaat Applications require:<br></strong>1. A completed Zakaat application form.<br>2. 2 forms of photo ID (passport/ ID card/ drivers permit)<br><br><strong>One off Housing Assistance (i.e. rent):<br></strong>A signed letter from the landlord indicating: <br>1.  Rental agreement<br>2. Monthly payment<br>3. Any arrears.<br>4. 1 form of ID for landlord<br>5. Utility bill for rental address in landlord\'s name.<br><br><strong>Medical Assistance:<br></strong>1. Doctor\'s letter confirming the diagnosis<br>2. Invoice for procedure</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary>I applied, what happens now?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>Once you have applied, a committee will review your application, and decide if we can help you. Once a decision is made, a representative will contact you to inform you of the decision.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Zakaat','','publish','closed','closed','','zakaat','','','2025-03-26 09:40:02','2025-03-26 09:40:02','',0,'http://phpilosophers.local/?page_id=206',0,'page','',0);
